W<-rnorm(600)
X<-numeric(600)
for (t in 2:600){
  X[t]<-X[t-1]+W[t]
}
plot(X, type="l", col="blue", lwd=2, xlab="t", ylab="X(t)")

adf.test(X)
## 
##  Augmented Dickey-Fuller Test
## 
## data:  X
## Dickey-Fuller = -2.7745, Lag order = 8, p-value = 0.2505
## alternative hypothesis: stationary
dX1<-diff(X)
plot(dX1, type="l", col="blue", lwd=2, xlab="t", ylab="dX(t)")

adf.test(dX1)
## Warning in adf.test(dX1): p-value smaller than printed p-value

W<-rnorm(600)
Y<-numeric(600)
for (t in 3:600){
  Y[t]<-2*Y[t-1]-Y[t-2]+1/3*W[t-1]+1/2*W[t-2]+W[t]
}
plot(Y, type="l", col="blue", lwd=2, xlab="t", ylab="Y(t)")

adf.test(Y)
## Warning in adf.test(Y): p-value greater than printed p-value
## 
##  Augmented Dickey-Fuller Test
